data.description: Welcome home to this 2nd story private, bright, and 1-level end-unit condo just 3 miles from the Battery! Fresh paint, updated light fixtures in every room, new flooring, new kitchen countertops, new finishes, new water heater, new HVAC! Nothing was overlooked. This spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bath home offers a master bedroom with en suite bathroom, and an open concept living space fitted with a fireplace for chilly evenings. The sunroom is a great spot to enjoy your morning coffee or unwind and relax after a long day. This friendly community features a pool, ample guest parking, and pleasant nature paths. This is the perfect location just moments from I-75/I-285, restaurants, shopping malls, great nature trails, bike paths, athletic clubs and more! Schedule your showing today!
